    <span xml:lang='en'>
      <strong>Some note about REISERFS/NTFS/JFS/EXT3 support in QTParted:</strong>
	Even if libparted does not support these filesystems QTParted can handle it.
	Of course it do it using external tools. This are the latest support status of
	this filesystems:
    </span>
  </p>

